FBIS4-60517 "drnes102_a_94001" FBIS-NES-94-102 Daily Report 25 May 1994 ARAB AFRICA Algeria Security Services Kill Two Assassin Suspects Security Services Kill Two Assassin Suspects LD2505160994 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1500 GMT 25 May 94 LD2505160994 Algiers Radio Algiers Network Arabic BFN [Text] The security services said in a statement today that its forces killed the two Hattab brothers and three other armed persons yesterday in the region of Ben Zerga, Boumerdes Province. The two Hattab brothers were wanted and were implicated in the assassination of the late Kasdi Merbah, the former prime minister and chairman of the Majd movement. They were also involved in the assassination of the late Mustafa Abeda, former director general of national television.
